# UI Package Implementation Rules

## Overview

The UI package provides a comprehensive design system built on Shadcn UI, offering reusable components, hooks, icons, and styling utilities for consistent user interfaces across all Proxed applications.

## Core Technologies

- **Components**: Shadcn UI v2 (Radix UI + Tailwind CSS)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 with CSS variables
- **Icons**: Custom icon components + Lucide React
- **Animation**: Tailwind Animate + Framer Motion
- **Build**: TypeScript with proper ESM exports

